---
title: "TrustLoop + Signatrust: AI Governance Pipeline"
---
flowchart TD
    subgraph GOVERN["🛡️ GOVERN (TrustLoop)"]
        direction TB
        A[AI Agent Request] --> B[TrustLoop Policy Check]
        B --> C{Decision}
        C -->|BLOCKED| D[❌ Action Denied]
        C -->|PENDING| E[⏳ Human Approval Required]
        C -->|ALLOWED| F[✅ Proceed]
    end

    subgraph EXECUTE["⚡ EXECUTE"]
        direction TB
        F --> G[Execute Action]
        E -->|Approved| G
    end

    subgraph PROVE["🔐 PROVE (Signatrust)"]
        direction TB
        G --> H[Generate Decision Receipt]
        H --> I[Ed25519 Signature]
        I --> J[SHA-256 Hash Chain]
        J --> K[Append-Only Ledger]
        K --> L[✅ Independently Verifiable]
    end

    subgraph SCENARIOS["📋 5 Production Workflows"]
        direction LR
        S1[💳 Payment Approval]
        S2[💰 Customer Refund]
        S3[🔒 PII Access]
        S4[📄 Document Generation]
        S5[👤 Human Approval]
    end

    style GOVERN fill:#1a237e,color:#fff
    style EXECUTE fill:#1b5e20,color:#fff
    style PROVE fill:#4a148c,color:#fff
